  "3126620": {
    "name": "Phantom Relics",
    "steam_appid": 3126620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.poster.avif?t=1769192018\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.webm?t=1769192018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/ee345bfbf522b12046208d48e6fc91ac.mp4?t=1769192018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>砍杀、射击、翻滚</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Phantom Relics</strong> 是一款<strong>快节奏等距视角砍杀游戏</strong>，拥有实时战斗、致命陷阱与<strong>爆炸性战斗</strong>。你可以独自一人，或与朋友进行本地合作闯入古老的地下墓穴，在对抗成群的不死怪物和强大 Boss 的过程中，阻止邪恶的觉醒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1769192018\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索、发现、思考</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了寻找可能拯救世界的强大遗物，你不仅需要与敌人战斗，还要解谜、躲避陷阱，并深入探索地牢中黑暗的角落。但别忘了 —— 每位 Boss 都拥有独特的攻击方式，并需要你<strong>采取特殊策略应对</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.poster.avif?t=1769192018\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.webm?t=1769192018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/6e31ee1680035414208794093033a31e.mp4?t=1769192018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 <strong>你将体验到</strong>：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>残酷战斗</strong> — 连击、格挡敌人攻击，并释放强力的终极技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>枪械武器</strong> — 使用霰弹枪或手枪射击；每个角色都有自己独特的武器风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>陷阱与爆炸</strong> — 躲避致命陷阱，利用爆炸桶等<strong>环境物品对抗敌人</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>本地合作</strong> — 本地分屏协作（或通过 Remote Play Together 联机），两位英雄共同深入一个被诅咒的地牢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>强大遗物</strong> — 收集 15 件以上独特的神器，改变你的战斗风格并解锁全新能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>史诗级 Boss 战</strong> — 每个 Boss 都有独特的攻击方式与战斗策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>黑暗奇幻氛围</strong> — 探索诡异阴森的地牢，揭示秘密，对抗不死怪、骑士与变异怪物的潮水攻势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126620/extras/65a1b70e99565593a47a75f13544bc8b.webp?t=1769192018\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>适合哪些玩家？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→ 喜欢<strong>反应速度与战术</strong>的砍杀游戏玩家。证明你无可战胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→ 热衷探索的玩家 —— 沉浸于黑暗奇幻氛围，揭开古老地穴的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >→ 本地合作狂热者 —— 一起清怪、卡关、分享药水……还有互相大喊大叫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 俄语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 韩语, 波兰语, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语, 日语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
